txt.en: Thank you for contributing your collection! Please place your items in the box to receive your reward.
Wanted: Blackened feathers from the birds near Trestlebridge. Deliver the items to Guardsman Otley in the town of Trestlebridge.
'These will be used to provide some measure of comfort for the people of Trestlebridge. Thank you.'
'Feathers from the wings are fine for stuffing part of the bed, but sometimes you need softer feathers.'
DNT HIDING CONTENT - Task: Blackened Feathers
Guardsman Otley, in Trestlebridge, is awaiting delivery of blackened feathers at the war-torn town of Trestlebridge.
Deliver the blackened feathers to Guardsman Otley at Trestlebridge
Wanted: Blackened feathers from the birds near Trestlebridge.
